Placeable
public class RestoredBackpack extends SlimefunBackpack
This class represents a SlimefunBackpack that has been restored via /sf backpack for retrieving items if the original has been lost. This backpack cannot be crafted nor crafted into other items. Its purpose is exclusively that of restoring the lost inventory and shouldn't be used as a backpack replacement. Right-Clicking will open the Inventory of the restored Backpack.
